title: Drake Maye on shoulder: I'm not trying to lie when I say I'm feeling great

sources.name: Pro Football Talk
sources.title: Drake Maye on shoulder: I'm not trying to lie when I say I'm feeling great
sources.description: The state of Patriots quarterback Drake Maye's right shoulder may have created some concern in the aftermath of New England's AFC Championship Game win over the Broncos, but there's been little reason for it this week.
